Intro3
------------------------------------------------------------------------
Doctors could not explain Marys condition, but her case was not unique. The Star Union considered Phaeton an off-limit planet and put it under quarantine due to its influence on human minds. 
A struggling but self-sustaining colony in the past, the city of Lydport lost all its population to mysterious epidemies of dementia and suicides in the recent years. 
The rector told you that Mary wanted to investigate the ruins of ancient monoliths scattered around the valley. When speaking, he avoided looking in your eyes. He did not seem to support her theory.


You talked to Mary for a week. Reminded her on your lectures, the expeditions, the excavation sites. Reflected your funny story behind the cosmodog. Nothing helped. She just sat there. Mindless. Absent. 


...